---
title: "工具"
breadcrumb:
  - name: "首页"
    href: "/"
  - name: "工具"
    href: "{{ page.url }}"
description: "14 个产品相关工具，覆盖图表、文档、AI 辅助等场景。"
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="tools-header">
  <h1>工具箱</h1>
  <p>14 个产品相关工具，覆盖图表、文档、AI 辅助等场景。</p>
</div>

<ul class="tool-list">
  {% for t in tools %}
  <li class="tool-item">
    {% if t.cmd %}<code class="tool-cmd">{{ t.cmd }}</code>{% endif %}
    <span class="tool-name">{{ t.name }}</span>
    <span class="tool-desc">{{ t.desc }}</span>
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

<section style="margin-top:40px;">
  <div class="section-heading">常用</div>
  <ul class="skill-list">
    <li class="skill-item">
      <code class="skill-cmd">/prd</code>
      <span class="skill-desc">最常用——写 PRD、功能文档、需求整理</span>
    </li>
    <li class="skill-item">
      <code class="skill-cmd">/meeting-to-action</code>
      <span class="skill-desc">整理会议纪要，提取行动项</span>
    </li>
    <li class="skill-item">
      <code class="skill-cmd">/obsidian-knowledge-saver</code>
      <span class="skill-desc">沉淀对话内容到知识库</span>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>
{% endblock %}
